item.title: This is the last post here
item.description: PSA: If you are around Malta, do SCUBA DIVING ! I had to add that before I close this blog for good. It did not last long did it? :D But it was nice the whole time <3 It was obvious for some time that I lost motivation composing posts here. Things did not progress in the pace I expected and I forgot the first part when the second finally happened, and I did not have the discipline to take notes and publish when ready.
